Github definition
--version control system
--have multiple versions for eg: today whatsapp version is 12.5 and tomorrow with new updates they are releasing new updates... similarly today we have 1 code and tomorrow i can modify/ update the code. that is next version...these can be doen using git hub. 
-- it helps to track the code changes... history codes
--used to collaborate on code.. eg: under one repository many people can work together on same code 

Github is a web based git reporsitory hosting services
* git is the backbone in that we have Github
* we have many alternatives for Github like Bitbucket, Gitbucket etc...
* but most companies use Github widely 

